                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="476681" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 30 Oct 2025 08:21:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After looking into the code, I know why &quot;debug&quot; and &quot;debug_mb&quot; can&apos;t be set with -P by lctl set_param, because they are LNET parameters, not Lustre system parameters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# find /sys/ -name debug_mb
/sys/kernel/debug/lnet/debug_mb
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These parameters of the libcfs kernel module are exposed via symlinks in /sys/kernel/debug/lnet/, not managed by MGS, at a lower layer than Lustre. So, we need to set them at module load time, for example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;modprobe libcfs libcfs_debug_mb=4096
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
